May be an image of 2 people, book and text that says 'The Man in the Arena NAVY SEAL CHIEF (RET.) EDDIE GALLAGHER and ANDREA GALLAGHER with Andy Symonds 深 "It's not the critic that counts." A BEO আ THE MAN IN THE ARENA FROM FIGHTINGISIS TO IGHTING FOR MY FREEDOM'.

node.text:
I am proud to have played a small role in the background of this story. Eddie is an incredible man and his much better half, Andrea - what a warrior. Lara and I are proud to call them both friends. 

I hope we never let woke politicians destroy the spirit of our incredible special forces. Thank God for them - they allow us to live in the greatest country on earth. 

Never allow this nonsense to happen again —

#TheManInTheArena 

🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸
